metadata.description: The Annawirral's Anti-Violence Artwork is a unique piece that centers around merging the interviewer with the Earth Mother, seeking a stronger voice through a deep exploration of the interviewer's thoughts and emotions to gain a deeper insight. By creating a new tradition between the interviewee and the Earth Mother, this work attempts to propose a new way to combat violence and create a community with motherly care
metadata.name: won't let you cry anymore #1
